PrimerMapper
======================

The README is used to introduce the module and scripts and provide 
instructions on how to install them, any machine dependencies it may
have (for example C compilers and installed libraries) and any other 
information that should be provided before the module is installed.

INSTALLATION

To install type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

The package require these modules and libraries:

  primer3
  Tkx
  Cwd
  Bio::SeqIO
  Bio::Graphics
  Bio::SeqFeature::Generic
  List::Util 'max'
  base 'Exporter'
  

